Nightmare Mudlib 3.2 SimulEfun: random_member()

varargs mixed random_member(mixed arr, int flag);

DESCRIPTION
Returns a random element from an array
If a mapping, it will return a random key from the mapping
If a mapping and flag is 1, it will return a random value from the mapping

LOCATION
/adm/simul_efun/random_member.c

SEE ALSO
member_array, map_delete, allocate
